        <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
        <p>Got questions? We've got answers. Here's everything you need to know about using SmartRetail effectively.</p>

        <div class="faq-container">
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <h3>How does SmartRetail forecast demand?</h3>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down"></i>
