                <p class="faq-answer">SmartRetail uses advanced machine learning models trained on historical sales data, seasonality, and external signals like holidays and weather to predict future demand accurately.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <h3>Can I customize inventory alerts?</h3>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down"></i>
