                <p class="faq-answer">Yes! You can set custom thresholds for low stock or overstock alerts, and SmartRetail will notify you when those conditions are met.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <h3>Is the dashboard real-time?</h3>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down"></i>
