            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <h3>Do I need technical expertise to use SmartRetail?</h3>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down"></i>
                </div>
                <p class="faq-answer">Not at all. SmartRetail is designed with simplicity in mind, offering an intuitive interface for managers, analysts, and business users alike.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
